ISLAMABAD, Apr 09 (APP): Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib said on Saturday that Foreign Minister Shah Mehmood Qureshi has offered to convene an in-camera meeting of the National Assembly and summoning the then Pakistani Ambassador to the United States.
In a tweet, he asked the opposition to accept this proposal so that the facts about the lettergate should be examined.
